        <item>
          <title>LeBron James breaks NBA mark for games played, Luke Kennard makes winning 3 in Lakers' win vs. Magic</title>
          <description><![CDATA[LeBron James set the NBA record by playing in his 1,612th regular-season game and Luke Kennard made a 3-pointer off a pass from James with 0.6 seconds left to send the Los Angeles Lakers to a 105-104 comeback victory over the Orlando Magic.]]></description>
